details.about: When it comes to real estate dealings, we deliver on truth & reliability. At Navya Developers, each of us are guided by the philosophy and vision of our founder, Mr Sridhara Reddy. Our core values of Integrity, Commitment and Customer-centricity are beacons for the way we all work. Each member of our leadership team has considerable experience in constructing and realising dream homes for our discerning customers.
